:"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeskeletoncomponenttokensprovider\/colors","title":"colors","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"colors"},{"kind":"text","text":": any "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllColorSemanticTokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of color semantic tokens to use for link colors"}]},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"title":"Theme Orange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeskeletoncomponenttokensprovider","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of skeleton"}],